#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.171"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.171:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.171:0.2"
msgid "18. Upāsakavagga "
msgstr "18. A Lay Follower "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.171:0.3"
msgid "171. Sārajjasutta "
msgstr "171. Timidity "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.171:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an5.171:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "an5.171:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "an5.171:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.171:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an5.171:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.171:2.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato upāsako sārajjaṃ okkanto hoti. "
msgstr "“A lay follower with five qualities is overcome by timidity. "

msgctxt "an5.171:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.171:2.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātī hoti, adinnādāyī hoti, kāmesumicchācārī hoti, musāvādī hoti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī hoti. "
msgstr "They kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, and use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. "

msgctxt "an5.171:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato upāsako sārajjaṃ okkanto hoti. "
msgstr "A lay follower with these five qualities is overcome by timidity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.171:3.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato upāsako visārado hoti. "
msgstr "A lay follower with five qualities is self-assured. "

msgctxt "an5.171:3.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.171:3.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti, musāvādā paṭivirato hoti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti. "
msgstr "They don’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. "

msgctxt "an5.171:3.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato upāsako visārado hotī”ti. "
msgstr "A lay follower with these five qualities is self-assured.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.171:3.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
